---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — RH Legal Services"
  description="Learn how RH Legal Services collects, uses, and protects your personal data in accordance with Colombian Law 1581 of 2012."
  lang="en"
  canonicalEs="/politica-privacidad"
  canonicalEn="/en/privacy-policy"
>
  <Navbar lang="en" currentPath="/en/privacy-policy" />

  <main class="pt-28 pb-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="mb-10">
        <span class="text-brand-500 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Legal Document</span>
        <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-navy-900 mt-3 mb-3">Privacy Policy & Personal Data Processing</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Last updated: January 2025</p>
      </div>

      <div class="prose prose-navy max-w-none text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-8">

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-3">1. Data Controller</h2>
          <p>
            <strong>RH Legal Services</strong> (hereinafter "RH Legal" or "the Firm"), domiciled in Colombia, is responsible for the processing of the personal data you provide through this website or any other means of communication.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3">Controller contact: <a href="mailto:info@rhlegales.com" class="text-brand-500 underline">info@rhlegales.com</a></p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-3">2. Legal Framework</h2>
          <p>
            This policy is governed by <strong>Statutory Law 1581 of 2012</strong> (Colombia's Personal Data Protection Act), <strong>Regulatory Decree 1377 of 2013</strong>, and other applicable concordant and complementary regulations.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-3">3. Personal Data We Collect</h2>
          <p>Through contact forms and other means, we may collect:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm">
            <li>Full name</li>
            <li>Email address</li>
            <li>Phone or mobile number</li>
            <li>Information about the service of interest</li>
            <li>Data you voluntarily share in communications</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-3">4. Purposes of Processing</h2>
          <p>Your personal data will be used to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm">
            <li>Respond to your legal advisory requests and inquiries.</li>
            <li>Provide contracted or prospective legal services.</li>
            <li>Send relevant information about our services (with your consent).</li>
            <li>Comply with applicable legal and regulatory obligations.</li>
            <li>Improve the quality of our services and communications.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-3">5. Your Rights as a Data Subject</h2>
          <p>Under Law 1581 of 2012, you have the right to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm">
            <li><strong>Access</strong> the personal data we hold about you.</li>
            <li><strong>Update and correct</strong> your data when inaccurate or incomplete.</li>
            <li><strong>Erasure</strong> of your data when no longer needed for the declared purpose.</li>
            <li><strong>Revoke</strong> the authorization granted for processing your data.</li>
            <li><strong>Access</strong> your data free of charge at least once per month.</li>
            <li><strong>File complaints</strong> with the Superintendence of Industry and Commerce (SIC) for violations of applicable regulations.</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm">To exercise your rights, send a request to: <a href="mailto:info@rhlegales.com" class="text-brand-500 underline">info@rhlegales.com</a></p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-3">6. Data Security</h2>
          <p>
            RH Legal adopts reasonable technical, human, and administrative measures to ensure the security of your personal data, preventing unauthorized access, loss, alteration, or improper disclosure.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-3">7. Transfer of Data to Third Parties</h2>
          <p>
            RH Legal does not sell, rent, or transfer your personal data to third parties without your consent, except where necessary for the delivery of contracted services (e.g., immigration authorities, SIC) or as required by law.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-3">8. Cookies & Tracking Technologies</h2>
          <p>
            This website may use cookies and similar technologies (such as Google Analytics / Google Tag Manager) to analyze traffic and improve user experience. You may configure your browser to reject cookies; however, some features may be affected.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-3">9. Policy Validity</h2>
          <p>
            This policy is effective from the date shown in its header. RH Legal reserves the right to modify it at any time. Material changes will be notified through this website.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-3">10. Contact</h2>
          <p>For any questions related to this policy or the processing of your data, contact us at:</p>
          <div class="mt-3 p-5 bg-gray-50 rounded-xl text-sm">
            <p><strong>RH Legal Services</strong></p>
            <p>Email: <a href="mailto:info@rhlegales.com" class="text-brand-500 underline">info@rhlegales.com</a></p>
            <p>Colombia</p>
          </div>
        </section>

      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer lang="en" />
</Layout>
